       01 ARCL5050-DATA.
          05 ARCL5050-INPUT.
             10 ARCL5050-EMAIL                     PIC X(50).
          05 ARCL5050-OUTPUT.
             10 ARCL5050-FLAG-EMAIL                PIC  X(01).
                88 ARCL5050-EMAIL-VALIDO              VALUE 'S'.
                88 ARCL5050-EMAIL-INVALIDO            VALUE 'N'.

       01 ARCL5050-ROTINA                 PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARM50050'.
